                                          Lodging

                                      .

                            Find a place to stay.

    The City of Kelso is a nutural "hub" to South West Washington & North
    West Oregon. Kelso is the place to stay when visiting the Northwest.
   Within minutes of most everything getting there is quick and fun. Come
     see Kelso and the rest of the Northwest, you wont be sorry you did.

